Marie Rappold https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie_Rappold 0 Marie Rappold, née Winterrath (17 August 1872 – 12 May 1957) was a German-born American operatic soprano. She sang with the Metropolitan Opera from 1905 to 1920. Marie_Rappold , née_Winterrath ( 17_August_1872 – 12_May_1957 ) was a_German-born_American_operatic_soprano .
